Packages 
Package Description
ie.gmit.sw.ai
Main package, contains the GameRunner which sets up the window and environment variables and the GameCtrl which controls most aspects of the game.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.audio
Manages audio for the game.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.characters
Manages the characters, which include the player and enemies.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.fight
Manages the fight system in the game.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.img
Manages the Images in the game.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.maze
Manages the maze generation, nodes and informed (heuristic) search algorithms (for path marking).
ie.gmit.sw.ai.traversers
Contains the Traverser abstract superclass.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.traversers.heuristic
Contains the informed (heuristic) search algorithms.
ie.gmit.sw.ai.traversers.uninformed
Contains the uninformed search algorithms.
